doc-94238ea0318c8c29cc15f73297bdb6b5.content: Albert Einstein was a famous theoretical physicist born in Ulm, Germany. He is best known for developing the Theory of Relativity, which revolutionized physics. Einstein won the Nobel Prize in Physics in 1921.
